These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, dancing
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, architect
1. the bartender is in an even position##4
2. the architect is the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | dancing | reading |
| Job     | architect    | bartender   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, surfing
1. the person who's sport is climbing is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | mirinda | milk        |
| Sport      | climbing  | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, d&b
There are 2 different nationalities: american, british
1. the american is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b    | disco |
| Nationality   | american | british |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, almond-milk
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, zucchini
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person eating zucchini is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | fanta      | almond-milk |
| Food       | raspberry | zucchini    |

 #################################

 
