.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, volleyball
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, train
1. the person driving the snowmobile is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Sport       | volleyball | ice-hockey  |
| Transport   | train  | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
